This paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories, as it deals with the training and compression of neural networks for image classification tasks. It may also be relevant to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories, as well as the computer architecture (cs.AR) sub-category, due to its focus on network acceleration and low bitwidth quantization.
